{"tid":551512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係一段關係裏面，主動嗰個人反而成為被動嗰個","createTime":"2018-02-05T17:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T00:08:53.000Z","uid":141175,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e536a8cf63d02462b2c1e0dfa1cc3563d7a3fbd1","tid":551512,"uid":141175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"係一段關係裏面，主動嗰個人反而成為被動嗰個<br />\n<br />\n聽落好似好矛盾，但請俾我解釋下。<br />\n有好多時當個男仔主動約女仔食飯，最終約唔約得成個主動權都係女仔手上，變咗就算男仔主動都冇用，都要個女仔肯先會食到飯。個女仔一日唔say yes，你一日都唔使旨意約到佢出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有同感"},{"pid":"1ae8ac235741064b960a86bf27e9c04a197d3927","tid":551512,"uid":2381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:48:33.000Z","msg":"我無唔俾你解釋喎"},{"pid":"a9bbd873241a4cae912e71eacba4a8ed5c88676e","tid":551512,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"咁你被動等佢約你食飯囉"},{"pid":"e2f21cce3e1f0d89791bd71f4075139c4b7b4af3","tid":551512,"uid":76098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:54:22.000Z","msg":"主導權同主動權有冇分別"},{"pid":"92a632a033359fcdc407645513f36e622756cc93","tid":551512,"uid":123170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:58:34.000Z","msg":"朋友嘅關係係咁㗎啦<br />\n係你條女都唔係老奉應約㗎啦"},{"pid":"a89a4acc824de2aa3d0944a1b65bb25d7695834c","tid":551512,"uid":144269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9bbd873241a4cae912e71eacba4a8ed5c88676e","tid":551512,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"咁你被動等佢約你食飯囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T18:00:00.000Z","msg":"咁就唔係主動同被動  動都動唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00c7050777ef2852d604cd4f5b9006f20aecfd9","tid":551512,"uid":135623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T18:04:24.000Z","msg":"&quot;要得到一個人，首先要證明你不需要她。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/f